description:
{{sbc|Innate - Goo:}} Every time '''Zac''' damages at least one enemy with an [[Champion ability|ability]], he sheds, depending on the ability, {{tt|a number of chunks|• Depending on the ability the amount of produced chunks can vary:&#013;
&nbsp;• Stretching Strikes: Maximum of 2 chunks, 1 chunk for each strike hit on a different target. The collision does not produce additional chunks.&#013;
&nbsp;• Unstable Matter: Maximum of 1 chunk, no matter how many enemies hit.&#013;
&nbsp;• Elastic Slingshot: Maximum of 5 chunks, 1 chunk for each enemy champion hit.&#013;
&nbsp;• Let's Bounce!: Maximum of 5 chunks, 1 chunk for each enemy champion hit. If the ability is charged for less than 1 second, only 1 chunk is produced.}} of himself to a nearby location, landing towards visible nearby enemy champions and lasting for 6 seconds.
